<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>New Ticket Created</title>
<style>
body {
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  background:#f4f6f8;
  padding:20px;
}
.container {
  max-width:600px;
  margin:auto;
  background:#ffffff;
  border-radius:8px;
  padding:25px;
  box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
}
.header {
  background:#2563eb;
  color:white;
  padding:15px;
  border-radius:6px;
  text-align:center;
  font-size:20px;
  font-weight:bold;
}
.content {
  margin-top:20px;
  color:#333;
}
.ticket-box {
  background:#f1f5f9;
  padding:15px;
  border-radius:6px;
  margin-top:15px;
}
.label {
  font-weight:bold;
}
.footer {
  margin-top:25px;
  font-size:12px;
  text-align:center;
  color:#777;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="container">

<div class="header">
🎫 New Ticket Raised
</div>

<div class="content">
<p>A new support ticket has been created.</p>

<div class="ticket-box">
<p><span class="label">Ticket Number:</span> {{ticketNumber}}</p>
<p><span class="label">Title:</span> {{title}}</p>
<p><span class="label">Description:</span> {{description}}</p>
<p><span class="label">Priority:</span> {{priority}}</p>
<p><span class="label">Category:</span> {{category}}</p>
<p><span class="label">Raised By:</span> {{raisedBy}} ({{raisedEmail}})</p>
</div>

<p>Please login to the admin panel to review the ticket.</p>
</div>

<div class="footer">
© {{currentYear}} Ticket System
</div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
